Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想在外面走動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是小雪入院治療的醫院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時隔半年的父子再會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渾身長滿棘刺的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.24,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我與你相逢在你的故事中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:44.33,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:44.33,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}憎惡背後滿載致命的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.01,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.01,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你是否會殺死朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果能滿足一己之願?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:52.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:52.24,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你是否願為他人而死?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:55.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:55.34,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}二者皆同義詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.91,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生存是場遊戲  即為倖存者  沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.50,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.50,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你將如何開始?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:03.23,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:03.23,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時空是穿過大門的十字路口!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:06.13,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:06.13,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你將去往何處?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.61,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.61,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你尋求著永恆之氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.53,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.53,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你為何而活?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:15.90,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:15.90,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們不知這個世界何時誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.77,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.77,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們是時空跳躍者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:20.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:20.78,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在這個世界裡 你一如往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:23.81,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:23.81,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一切將遵循著既定規則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:28.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:28.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是啊,我們在愛的交織中穿梭於過去及未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:29.28,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:29.28,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爆發!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:34.33,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:34.33,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}讓我們回撥一切傷痛繼而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.95,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.95,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想和你一起看群星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:40.01,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:40.01,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}穿越奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:46.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
